ed="T" n="0760a10"/><persName key="A010198">釋藏師</persName>，姓<name>王</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000001058">趙郡</placeName>人也。父為<placeName key="PL000000016494"><anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>毫</sic><corr>亳</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz1"/>州</placeName>掾。稚<lb
ed="T" n="0760a11"/>齒尋師，居然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1424"/>慕法，而性好獨處。<placeName key="PL000000016494">譙</placeName>多厲鬼，<lb
ed="T" n="0760a12"/>持魅於人。<persName key="A010198">藏</persName>七歲，隻影閑房<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1425"/>，孤形逈野<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1426"/>，甞<lb
ed="T" n="0760a13"/>無少畏。至年長，彌見挺拔，故號<persName key="A010198">降魔藏</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760a14"/>歟。請列青衿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g591"/>于<placeName key="PL000000016487">廣福院</placeName><persName key="A012441">明讚<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，<ref type="person" target="#A012441">師</ref>意其法<lb
ed="T" n="0760a15"/>器，乃發擿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1427"/><ref type="person" target="#A010198">之</ref>，譍對辯給，答出問表。因留執<lb
ed="T" n="0760a16"/>事，服勤受法，俾誦《法華》，踰月徹部，登即<lb
ed="T" n="0760a17"/>剃落，受具習律焉。次講南宗論，大機<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1428"/>將發。<lb
ed="T" n="0760a18"/>俄投麈尾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g796"/>，<placeName key="PL000000000083">九州</placeName>靈跡罕不登升。後往遇北<lb
ed="T" n="0760a19"/><anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>州</sic><corr>宗</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz2"/>鼎盛，便誓依棲。<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>問曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010198">汝</ref>名<persName key="A010198">降魔</persName>，<ref type="person" target="#A009582">我</ref>此<lb
ed="T" n="0760a20"/>無山精木怪，<ref type="person" target="#A010198">汝</ref>翻作魔邪？」曰：「有佛有魔。」<persName key="A009582">秀</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760a21"/>云：「<ref type="person" target="#A010198">汝</ref>若是魔，必住不思議境界也。」曰：「是佛<lb
ed="T" n="0760a22"/>亦空，何不思議之有？」時眾莫不異而欽<ref type="person" target="#A010198">之</ref>。<lb
ed="T" n="0760a23"/>先是<persName key="A009582">秀<roleName>師</roleName></persName>懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/>之：「<ref type="person" target="#A010198">汝</ref>與<ref type="place" target="#PL000000021501">少皞之墟</ref><ptr target="#n1373"/>有緣。」尋<lb
ed="T" n="0760a24"/>入<placeName key="PL000000021580">泰山</placeName>數年，學者臻萃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1405"/>，供億<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1227"/>克周，為<placeName key="PL000000020275">金輿谷</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0760a25"/><persName key="A002192">朗<roleName>公</roleName></persName>行化之亞也。一日，告門人曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010198">吾</ref>今老<lb
ed="T" n="0760a26"/>朽，物極有歸，正是其時。」言訖而終。春秋九<lb
ed="T" n="0760a27"/>十一矣。</p>
